      "instruction": "<p>Boil a full kettle</p><p>Peel and finely slice 1/2 <span class=\"text-danger\">[1] </span><strong>brown onion</strong>, then grate the rest</p><p>Dissolve <strong>half</strong> the<strong> chicken stock mix</strong> (save the rest for later!) in 200ml <span class=\"text-danger\">[350ml] </span><strong>boiled water </strong>and add the <strong>sultanas</strong> – this is your <strong>sultana stock</strong></p>",
