    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine the <strong>lean</strong> <strong>beef mince</strong> in a large bowl with the <strong>grated onion</strong>, <strong>panko breadcrumbs</strong>, <strong>cayenne pepper</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!),<strong> half</strong> the <strong>ground cumin</strong> (save the rest for later!) and a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Divide the mixture into 10 <span class=\"text-danger\">[20]</span> and shape into meatballs</p>",
